# Terminal

- Panel visible without starting a PTY; process starts only on explicit open/task.
- Bounded scrollback; viewport render only; no images/ligatures by default.
- Close kills process tree unless detached.
- See `docs/velocity/12-terminal-ram-and-process-management.md`.
